    "Firstly, our study uses twice as many IAD datasets as Tao et al. [2] Secondly, we analyze the performance of IAD using the most comprehensive image level and pixel level metrics.",
    "Nevertheless, Cui et al. [3] and Tao et al.",
    "[2] only employ image level metrics, neglecting the anomalies localization performance of IAD.",
    "Thirdly, our study develops a taxonomy based on the design of neural network architecture with varying degrees of supervision.",
